snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin DS Touch de Dokodon - Flight of the Bumblebee (Rimsky-Korsakov) [Demon-level]
snippet.description:
Here I am trying to get a golden crown at Flight of the Bumblebee in Demon mode but failing stupidly. It's been a couple of years since I recorded this and haven't played Taiko since then. Sadly.
------
Esta soy yo intentando conseguir la corona de oro en el Flight of the Bumblebee en modo Demonio pero fallando estúpidamente. Este vídeo lo filmé hace unos años y no he vuelto a jugar al Taiko desde entonces. Tristemente.
